<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٥٥٧ - ل ز ب]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لزِبَ يلزَب، لَزَبًا، فهو لَزِب<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• لزِب الشَّيءُ:</span> لزَب؛ ثبت واشتدّ <span class="c1">"لزِب الطِّينُ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• لزِب الطِّين:</span> لزَب؛ لزِق وتماسك.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>